    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Beginning at 14th level, you have learned to utilize your healing abilities in larger bursts.</p><p> When you would use your Field Surgery feature to heal a creature, you can double the amount of Physician Dice you use, healing all creatures within 15 feet of the target creature an amount of hit points equal to half the result of the dice rolled.</p><p> Beginning at 17th level, when you use this feature, you can choose which creatures are healed.</p><p></p>",
